<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bienvenue sur Equita-Planner</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: #003366;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .email-header img {
            max-width: 150px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .email-content {
            padding: 30px;
           
        }
        .email-content h1 {
            color: #003366;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .reset-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #003366;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .reset-button:hover {
            background-color: #004488;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            color: #666;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            font-size: 0.8em;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="email-header">
            <% if (typeof logoUrl !== 'undefined' && logoUrl) { %>
                <img src="<%= logoUrl %>" alt="Logo de l'application">
            <% } %>
        </div>
        
        <div class="email-content">
          <h1><%= locals.stableName %> vient de t'accepter</h1> 
          <p>Bonjour <%= locals.name %>,</p>
          <p>Ton compte Equita-Planner a été rattaché à <%= locals.stableName %>.</p> 
        </div>
        <div class="email-content">
            <p>Connecte-toi sur Equita-Planner pour commencer à planifier tes prochaines leçons.</p>
            <a href="<%= locals.url %>" class="reset-button">Je me connecte</a>
          </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Votre Application. Tous droits réservés.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>